{
  "comment": "Решение:\n\\( \\cfrac{-12}{(x-1)^2-2} \\geqslant 0 \\)\n\\( \\Rightarrow (x-1)^2-2<0\\), так как \\( -12<0 \\) и \\( \\cfrac{-12}{(x-1)^2-2} \\geqslant 0 \\)\n\\( (x-1)^2-2<0 \\)\n\\( (x-1)^2-(\\sqrt{2})^2<0 \\)\n\\( (x-1-\\sqrt{2})(x-1+\\sqrt{2})<0 \\)\n\\( (x-1-\\sqrt{2})(x-1+\\sqrt{2})=0 \\)\n\\( x-1-\\sqrt{2}=0 \\) или \\( x-1+\\sqrt{2}=0 \\)\n\\( x=1+\\sqrt{2 } \\) или \\( x=1-\\sqrt{2} \\)\nОтвет: \\( x \\in (1-\\sqrt{2};1+\\sqrt{2}) \\)",
